      </section>
      <section eId="section_7">
        <heading><b>Annex B – Hansard references</b></heading>
        <paragraph>
          <num>37 </num>
          <content>
            <p>The following table sets out the dates and Hansard references for each stage of the Act’s passage through Parliament.</p>
            <table ukm:widths="2.25in 1.34in 2.16in">
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Stage</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Date</b></p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><b>Hansard reference</b></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td colspan="3">
                  <p><i>House of Commons</i></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Introduction</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>15 June 2022</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://publications.parliament.uk/pa/bills/cbill/58-03/0027/220027.pdf"><u>Bill as introduced</u></a></p>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/2022-06-15/debates/10ed5b44-97ae-46cb-ab4c-f87f0aa7c33c/CommonsChamber"><u>Vol. 716 col. 315</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Second Reading</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>09 December 2022</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2022-12-09/debates/C787785F-B63E-422A-81BB-A3F3534B4575/ChildSupport(Enforcement)Bill"><u>Vol. 724 col. 664</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
                <td>
                  <p>Public Bill Committee</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p>14 December 2022</p>
                </td>
                <td>
                  <p><a href="https://hansard.parliament.uk/commons/2023-03-01/debates/52b49271-3a84-4cb6-9683-484548c337b6/ChildSupport(Enforcement)Bill"><u>Col. 1</u></a></p>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr>
